**Problem73 (K-map, 4 variable)**

source:https://hdlbits.01xz.net/wiki/Kmap2

Exercise:
module top_module(
    input a,
    input b,
    input c,
    input d,
    output out  ); 
    assign out=(!a&!d)|(!b&!c)|b&c&d|a&c&d;

endmodule


**Problem74 (K-map, 4 variable with don't care)**

Source:https://hdlbits.01xz.net/wiki/Kmap3

Exercise:
module top_module(
    input a,
    input b,
    input c,
    input d,
    output out  ); 
    assign out= a|(!b&c);
endmodule


**Problem75 (K-map, 4 variable-exclusive)**

Source:https://hdlbits.01xz.net/wiki/Kmap4

Exercise:
module top_module(
    input a,
    input b,
    input c,
    input d,
    output out  ); 
	assign out=a^b^c^d;
endmodule
